                Black for the people. Gold for the wealth. Green for the land. Red for the blood. Blue for the peace.
            </p>
      </div>

      <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-700">
